如留力到入棺材果日啦7頭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:51:34.000Z","msg":"現時我只係睇到，大部份人被拉，被打死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n叫你打遊擊戰，敵進我退，敵駐我擾，敵疲我打"},{"pid":"112f09517be66082ed977956a065b7b86c4260cd","tid":1605964,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:52:54.000Z","msg":"除非陳雲上台"},{"pid":"d143b0f5a1255b8cbfad17038b2f76b12ba860ad","tid":1605964,"uid":61161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:53:31.000Z","msg":"掘磚嘅你哋...點解唔一人一罐可樂？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1603698\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1603698</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fa9ab7cf270c71603c331b77ac597e4fe7df0ed8","tid":1605964,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:09:57.000Z","msg":"泛民害死人，要人去港島。外國善人收到可靠情報，明日香港會變成衙差統治，但疑是泛民的人依然號召義民去港島被圍捕。<br />\n泛民的人出來也許沒事（如果真的夠一百萬人出來反共而不是慶祝國慶），義民出去就會被打被殺被姦，之後泛民去美國領功。<br />\n外國人想救香港人，但香港人害死自己人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/71388281_2378033479180927_8049150728570142720_o.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;_nc_oc=AQkbx_m6Im6HYE9kaUGN-tuF5YXjLOFR1DRORyKVJv0a7Ypt4eD9uaJvBDuq2wL-FHw&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=468cd6767bb90493447dd4a86041a335&amp;oe=5E35FA0E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F71388281_2378033479180927_8049150728570142720_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D104%26_nc_oc%3DAQkbx_m6Im6HYE9kaUGN-tuF5YXjLOFR1DRORyKVJv0a7Ypt4eD9uaJvBDuq2wL-FHw%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3D468cd6767bb90493447dd4a86041a335%26oe%3D5E35FA0E&h=2920eaea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/71594261_10157450750882225_7258814198497411072_n.jpg?_nc_cat=100&amp;_nc_oc=AQmzsZ72EctqGdnRsrFfGihtUKylEUS-1Srqmu7S3a62bUVYHQIP_owgzJKMKEYcV6A&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=e6023b31658274eecd88ee01eddbc009&amp;oe=5E37520F\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F71594261_10157450750882225_7258814198497411072_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D100%26_nc_oc%3DAQmzsZ72EctqGdnRsrFfGihtUKylEUS-1Srqmu7S3a62bUVYHQIP_owgzJKMKEYcV6A%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3De6023b31658274eecd88ee01eddbc009%26oe%3D5E37520F&h=91121496&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ae157a87365944af5547f7665ef3f928a672ec16","tid":1605964,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:12:24.000Z","msg":"I&rsquo;m gonna get into this more soon, but seriously, no need to stand around provoking the police anymore. There&rsquo;s nothing Protesters can do that will make them more aggressive, so as to shame them. They are unshameable<br />\nSurrounding police stations is now akin to standing in one spot and getting beaten like in 2014. <br />\n<ins><span style=\"color: red;\">Focus should now be on turning HK into a full on city in rebellion. That means political graffiti on a level never experienced before, all topped off with targeted guerrilla tactics with precise targets and exit strategies.</span></ins><br />\nThe police tactic is now, let protesters gather, let a few of them break the law and then this gives them the pretext to stop anyone, anywhere on suspicion of committing a crime at a protest. <br />\nOnce there was a time to come together as a gigantic wave. Now is the time to make it rain all across HK.<br />\n<br />\n人地外國人俾既advice都係咁,你地自己要送死，沒人阻止，但唔該唔好送其他人死"},{"pid":"83f301ae0a61ef9535ff5f1ff4504c2646fd8a59","tid":1605964,"uid":117893,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f74f92d05119424f81adf728e885678648bbcc8f","tid":1605964,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:40:38.000Z","msg":"除非陳雲上台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:13:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}